thread.title: BRIEF-Jordan's Islamic Insurance Company FY Profit Rises

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jordan's Islamic Insurance Company FY Profit Rises

organizations.name: islamic insurance company fy profit rises feb

text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - ISLAMIC INSURANCE COMPANY:
* FY NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE TO SHAREHOLDERS 2 MILLION DINARS VERSUS 1.9 MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* FY NET OPERATING REVENUE 17.1 MILLION DINARS VERSUS 16.3 MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* BOARD PROPOSES FY CASH DIVIDEND OF 8 PERCENT FROM CO'S PAID IN CAPITAL Source: ( bit.ly/2H0jiQK ) Source: ( bit.ly/2GVxrhP ) Further company coverage: )
